{"word":"ἀποκνέω","slug":"ἀποκνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποκνέω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to shrink from</i> danger, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: —<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to shrink from</i> doing, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to shrink back, hesitate</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}